sdata.j: ↑温度↑↓おんど↓は|↑七↑↓なな↓↑十|↑↓じゅう↓↑度↑↓ど↓です。
そんな↑失敗↑↓しっぱい↓なんて↑気↑↓き↓にするな。↑人↑↓ひと↓の↑噂↑↓うわさ↓も|↑七↑↓なな↓↑十|↑↓じゅう↓↑五↑↓ご↓↑日↑↓にち↓。みんなすぐに↑忘↑↓わす↓れるさ。
sdata.e: I wouldn't let a goof-up like that get to you. People have short memories and the one good thing about gossip is that it's short-lived.

sdata.j: ↑確↑↓たし↓かに|↑七↑↓なな↓↑十|↑↓じゅう↓はすぎてる。

sdata.e: Nine hundred twenty-five billion, eight hundred fourteen million, seven hundred three thousand, six hundred ninety-two is a twelve-digit number.
